caption: Travel nurses! We get it. Moving every 12 weeks can be tricky -- it's important to make your new environment feel comfortable and familiar, even if it’s temporary. Sometimes, you just need to sit down with your favorite mug huddled in your worn-in sweatshirt and turn on your go-to comfort show. We’ve got you covered with our stellar packing list. Let's make your new home feel like home and prepare you for any new adventure! 💗 Did we miss anything? Comment below 👇
